Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:06.48,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}飞舞在宇宙 化作繁星点点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:12.36,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}光が切ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:12.36,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}光芒一明一灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:18.24,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}踏み締めた足元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:18.24,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}向前迈出脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:24.12,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}揺らいでしまうから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:24.12,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}却不能稳立于咆哮的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:30.33,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}手を伸ばしてくれたあの頃を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:30.33,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}你向我伸出援手的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:36.63,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}思い出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:36.63,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}在思念的深海中苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:44.35,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}キラリ星屑たち 集めてみても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:44.35,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}我尝试集聚那闪耀的星尘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:50.35,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}涙 ぽろぽろぽろ こぼれて 消え入るそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:50.35,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}但泪水扑簌而下 消失其间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:56.03,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}ぎゅっと指の隙間 胸に当てたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:56.03,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}紧握的手指之间 是我炽热的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:03.12,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}何時か 砕け散った約束を リングに変える
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:03.12,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(40,200)}终有一天 散碎的约定就是连接你我的丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.17,0:27:07.64,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}目を覚ましたとき いつもの癖で「おはよう」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.17,0:27:07.64,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}酣梦初醒 一如往常问早安
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.43,0:27:20.99,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}あと何度 同じ泣きそうな顔させるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.43,0:27:20.99,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}曾经几回 为君而面露哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:34.88,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}その運命は まるで蛍火のように見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:34.88,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}命若萤火 过眼云烟转瞬逝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.84,0:27:49.48,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}風を泳ぐように 心を揺らすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.84,0:27:49.48,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}心乱情惘 如若游弋狂风中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.94,0:28:02.99,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}何度も 何度も 問いかけても
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.94,0:28:02.99,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}曾几回 曾几回 寻踪觅迹
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.20,0:28:10.29,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}鏡に写る日々は 答えくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.20,0:28:10.29,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}杳然无信 镜中倒影无回音
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.62,0:28:19.88,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}いつかは 消えた未来もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.62,0:28:19.88,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}断缘再续 终将有时
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.59,0:28:26.35,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}信じたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.59,0:28:26.35,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}心诚则明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触碰了这所学校诅咒的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神会被慢慢侵蚀 陷入错乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会毫不犹豫对其他人下手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 不过症状因人而异
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后肉体会像焦炭一样染成黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而灵魂会被困在这所天神小学里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这种现象称为黑化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友触碰了诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为了守护内心而做了激烈的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后选择了自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你朋友一死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这所学校的活人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只剩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孑然一人到死为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经回不到原来的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能像一起过来的朋友一样静静等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起？ 茧也在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茧在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茧在哪里？ 回不去到底是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神町奉知报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天神小学屡屡发生的可怕的犯罪事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几个月来在町内发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「儿童连续失踪事件」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经有关部门侦查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就以最糟糕的情况草草结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭和48年9月18日晚上7点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在校内发现了失踪儿童的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及一名手持着沾血的剪刀 精神恍惚的教师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此人目前已被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是篠崎说过的杀人事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们为什么会在这个天神小学里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神小学应该在很久之前就被拆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我们穿越到过去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 我都会保护由香的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先去找找大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定直美他们也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香 想去上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一个看着能用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香还能忍一会 去找找别的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我们也会变成那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 一定能回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森繁！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去刚死没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不管这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我们 好像还有别的学校的学生被传过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是一些精神严重错乱的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说都没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不快点的话 我们也会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得是 我们分头去找大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去的办法到时候再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 那我去找茧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到人的话就让他到前面的紧急出口集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 持田 差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有幽灵 你们小心一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是案件的受害者 我看到过一次 伤得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候幽灵正在袭击其他学校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵会袭击？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还有一个跟我们年纪差不多的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过应该是无害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别离开我啊 由香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 篠崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头 头快要炸开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再呆在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 振作一点 振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的脸在报纸里看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要和那家伙对视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能对视！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道.....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来这！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥和姐姐 你们谁先想死呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先弄死谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先弄死姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就先弄死你好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你也有灵媒体质
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你救了我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这身校服我没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我们一样也被关在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经死在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来这里寻找重要的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你是七星同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女高中生灵能师 冴之木七星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在灵能探讨和心灵情报的主页上非常出名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 七星同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在关注你的网站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从「幸福的幸子」那个帖子之后就再也没有更新 我一直很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然发生了这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你刚刚说是来这边找人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那既然能来 就肯定有回去的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的话就快点告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在死去之前 为了逃离而全力调查了这所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看上去形成这个异空间——天神小学的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那4名连续诱拐杀害事件的受害儿童的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上报纸里的那个报道里的那些小孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的那个也是其中之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我半途中力竭而倒下 所以没能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是能平息那些孩子的灵魂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这个空间就会崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能就会不再虐待我们 把我们放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让灵魂平息这种事情要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先凶手的忏悔是必须的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个凶手也在这个学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忏悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对那样的家伙我和篠崎又能做…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友也在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才进来的灵魂有9个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9个 大家都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶快去找他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能找得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是可怕的诅咒形成的多重闭锁空间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多重闭锁空间？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在同一个地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不在一个次元就绝对见不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果是你的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个教室是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理科教室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿童的死因是被被捕教室用大裁缝剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪掉舌头失血过多或者窒息而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇害儿童中 有一人在死后被切掉头部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丧心病狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃本同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 她就是我最喜欢的结衣老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也很喜欢学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃..铃本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很喜欢老师 跟你们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃本同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离那些小孩远…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两个都不是坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很可怜的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个老师也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 我无法放下这些孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我会留在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 铃本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧出去和大家会合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森繁同学也在为你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繁哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快点一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃本同学是我可爱的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃本同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃本…同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重要的…学生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能保护好她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪啊 茧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你若不陪在我身边 就让我心如刀绞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我一直这么想 但这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茧…你的容颜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你喊我繁哥哥的声音让我得到的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别扔下我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 不看看别人的不幸就不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过得还算不错 还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 嘿嘿 收集了好多尸体的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议 明明都是真的 看上去却很假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这个才是最华丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这堆肉酱真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也曾是活生生的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 现在不是做这种事情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有来电显示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像能听到什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要看我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看我 不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看我的内脏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繁哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也没法用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…就是森繁说的幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看上去没有受伤的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在这里迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 她说让我们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么小的孩子也被困在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个门外面有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才过来的时候这边应该没有门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香快憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在这里解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这种高度应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香 千万不要接近树林
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你能陪我一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先进去等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事了大声喊我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白檀高等学校 刻命裕也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 森繁也说过这里有其他学校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也和我们一样做了幸子的咒语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不开 为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你在哪里？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回一声啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在多重闭锁空间里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们或许无法见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果持田他们能够看见这个蜡烛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就可能告诉他我们也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 义雄就是那个凶手教师的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人偶可能就是那个凶手的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是要我们通过人偶来获得凶手的忏悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这人偶长得真渗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉随时都会开口说话 真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对..不..起..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人..人偶说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 岸沼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了那么多孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的精神出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有打算杀他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 岸沼..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音能当做凶手的忏悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是装在袋子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉泽辽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得遇害儿童里面有个叫这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我看看..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 吉泽辽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是刚才袭击我们的小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}还给我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又蹦出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是吉泽辽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的…还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是说「还给我」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的舌头...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那样算是平息了那个小鬼的灵魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼你拿到的是那个孩子被凶手切掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还有三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须找到他们的舌头还给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点的话 人偶还会告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.12,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(28.667,32.667)}管乃雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.12,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(151.333,59.333)}辻时子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.12,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(28,90)}吉泽辽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不怕那些幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:21:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是强装镇定而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是怪某些人靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好..好了 就剩一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得名字叫篠崎幸子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是没错……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是根据报道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸子应该在遭到杀害之前就被发现了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕用对付辽的办法是无法让她平息的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平息什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子不是没事么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那她就应该好好活着 变成老太婆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 所有的孩子都得到平息了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是什么都没有发生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 原来是钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害人吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之这算是告一段落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得还有什么重要的事情还没做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是持田的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 脑袋变得好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都是这样的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥...哥哥 不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你在瑟瑟发抖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来吧 我跟你一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.93,0:23:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香自己去找...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说帮你去找你哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但...但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这孩子真不懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了 我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别躲着了 快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事跟你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.11,0:24:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个时候跟茧也约好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约好了要永远在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也变成茧那样让我收在手机里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 茧子就不会寂寞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里 你快出来吧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.96,0:24:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.44,0:24:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方捉迷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚在说「哥哥」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.44,0:24:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我和哥哥走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.53,0:24:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也在找妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.33,0:24:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 我们一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.96,0:25:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是白檀高等学校二年级的刻命裕也
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.85,0:25:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是持田由香
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.03,0:25:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是因为幸子的咒语被困在这里了么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.21,0:25:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那个 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.99,0:25:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.00,0:25:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.30,0:25:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到我这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.38,0:25:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.80,0:25:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.14,0:25:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.27,0:25:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以刚才才躲起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.66,0:25:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.35,0:25:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要来手机里陪茧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.61,0:25:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.64,0:25:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香你待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.20,0:26:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.55,0:26:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你可是我最重要的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.30,0:26:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
